the next few decades we are going to have

00:21:09.980 --> 00:21:12.799
to radically change how we do computing.

00:21:12.799 --> 00:21:17.220
So this take comes at it from the theoretical
limit perspective rather than looking at our

00:21:17.220 --> 00:21:18.980
