like pills or in every device here giving

00:22:55.220 --> 00:23:02.360
an IP address to the lights and other things
that don't need to be connected by wiring.

00:23:02.360 --> 00:23:07.070
The revolution that I'm talking about is being
driven by a confluence of trends.

00:23:07.070 --> 00:23:12.730
So it's the efficiency of computing but also
the efficiency of communications and the efficiency

00:23:12.730 --> 00:23:13.850
of sensors.

00:23:13.850 --> 00:23:19.909
So as we get MEMS devices that can do sensing
at very low power levels then you get all

00:23:19.909 --> 00:23:22.850
sorts of interesting things that we couldn't
do before, and then, of course, efficiency

00:23:22.850 --> 00:23:24.249
