important as well.

00:23:32.880 --> 00:23:38.419
In most of these devices, the bulk of the
electricity use is actually in idle mode.

00:23:38.419 --> 00:23:44.840
So the active power is not the most critical
thing in many cases, it's actually how fast

00:23:44.840 --> 00:23:50.390
can you put the device to sleep and how low
can you make the power use go?

00:23:50.390 --> 00:23:56.190
So the engineering challenges are different
from building the fastest computer at its

00:23:56.190 --> 00:24:00.759
