also almost invariably improve energy efficiency

00:24:45.350 --> 00:24:46.350
of computing.

00:24:46.350 --> 00:24:51.090
We're far from the theoretical limits but,
as all of you know, there are some technological

00:24:51.090 --> 00:24:54.360
challenges that we're facing in the coming
years.

00:24:54.360 --> 00:25:00.350
The biggest implications of these trends is
