00:36:36.730 --> 00:36:37.730
to the infrastructure.

00:36:37.730 --> 00:36:38.730
&gt;&gt;male #6: Okay, thank you.

00:36:38.730 --> 00:36:40.430
&gt;&gt;Jon Koomey: The cooling, fans, pumps, everything
